{"title_hebrew":"שער הרחמים","title_english":"Sha'ar HaRachamim (Gate of Mercy)","artist":"Meir Banai","overview":"A soulful ballad about wandering in Jerusalem and finding the Gate of Mercy. It describes a simple man seeking meaning and redemption, declaring that life ultimately has a purpose.","youtube_url":"https://youtu.be/9vweQZfJKBo?si=ALSfqrNwz1c7KZtf","lyrics":[{"hebrew":"מסתובב בעיר הישנה","transliteration":"Mistovev ba'ir hayeshana","english":"Walking around the Old City"},{"hebrew":"ורעש בא מכל פינה","transliteration":"Vera'ash ba mikol pina","english":"And noise comes from every corner"},{"hebrew":"אני מכיר כבר את הדרך","transliteration":"Ani makir kvar et haderech","english":"I already know the way"},{"hebrew":"בדרך לשער הרחמים","transliteration":"Baderech leSha'ar HaRachamim","english":"On the way to the Gate of Mercy"},{"hebrew":"לא מביט סביב","transliteration":"Lo mabit saviv","english":"I don't look around"},{"hebrew":"לא מקשיב","transliteration":"Lo makshiv","english":"I don't listen"},{"hebrew":"איש חולם אני","transliteration":"Ish cholem ani","english":"I am a dreamer"},{"hebrew":"וכך היה תמיד","transliteration":"Vekach haya tamid","english":"And so it always was"},{"hebrew":"אבל מכיר כבר את הדרך","transliteration":"Aval makir kvar et haderech","english":"But I already know the way"},{"hebrew":"בדרך לשער הרחמים","transliteration":"Baderech leSha'ar HaRachamim","english":"On the way to the Gate of Mercy"},{"hebrew":"חי פעם רק פעם","transliteration":"Chai pa'am, rak pa'am","english":"Live once, only once"},{"hebrew":"יש טעם אין טעם","transliteration":"Yesh ta'am, ein ta'am","english":"There is meaning, there is no meaning"},{"hebrew":"עם כוח בלי כוח","transliteration":"Im koach, bli koach","english":"With strength, without strength"},{"hebrew":"שער הרחמים","transliteration":"Sha'ar HaRachamim","english":"Gate of Mercy"},{"hebrew":"בואי איתי יחד","transliteration":"Boi iti yachad","english":"Come with me together"},{"hebrew":"בואי מתוך הפחד","transliteration":"Boi mitoch hapachad","english":"Come from within the fear"},{"hebrew":"כי את, גם את חלק","transliteration":"Ki at, gam at chelek","english":"Because you, you are also part"},{"hebrew":"משער הרחמים","transliteration":"Misha'ar HaRachamim","english":"Of the Gate of Mercy"},{"hebrew":"השלטים מעל החנויות","transliteration":"Hashlatim me'al hachanuyot","english":"The signs above the shops"},{"hebrew":"משקיפים על הרחובות","transliteration":"Mashkifim al harchovot","english":"Overlook the streets"},{"hebrew":"בתוך ליבי יש צעקה והיא גדולה","transliteration":"Betoch libi yesh tze'aka vehi gdola","english":"Inside my heart there is a scream and it is big"},{"hebrew":"הראו לי את שער הרחמים","transliteration":"Har'u li et Sha'ar HaRachamim","english":"Show me the Gate of Mercy"}]}